      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/NaturraumregionenSTMK/uMzT",
    "@type": [
      "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept"
    ],
    "http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo": [
      {
        "@id": "http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/applicationschema/br"
      }
    ],
    "http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject": [
      {
        "@id": "http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/theme/br"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Well-established name for the Muerztal below the narrowness of Wartberg (breakthrough valley), which, like the Middle Muerztal, is an inner-alpine basin consisting of fluvial and fluvioglacial sediments of the Quaternary period in the actual valley area and of tertiary loose material at the edges, where gentle slope drags and reed beds are situated in front of the neighboring mountain bodies. The Tertiary depression of Parschlug, which reaches back into the Muerztal Alps and is attributed to the basin of the Lower Muerztal, should be emphasized. (Author: Prof. Mag. Dr. Gerhard Karl LIEB)"
      },
      {
        "@language": "de",
        "@value": "Gut eingebuergerte Bezeichnung fuer das Muerztal unterhalb der Enge von Wartberg (Durchbruchstal), das ebenso wie das Mittlere Muerztal ein inneralpines Becken darstellt, welches aus fluvialen und fluvioglazialen Sedimenten des Quartaers im eigentlichen Talraum und aus tertiaeren Lockermateralien an den Raendern besteht, wo sanfte Hangschleppen und Riedel den benachbarten Gebirgskoerpern vorgelagert sind. Hervorzuheben ist die in die Muerztaler Alpen zurueckgreifende Tertiaermulde von Parschlug, die dem Becken des Unteren Muerztales zugerechnet wird. (Verfasser: Prof. Mag. Dr. Gerhard Karl LIEB)"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme": [
      {
        "@id": "https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/NaturraumregionenSTMK"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation": [
      {
        "@value": "uMzT"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel": [
      {
        "@language": "de",
        "@value": "Unteres Muerztal"
      },
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Lower Muerztal"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "INSPIRE governance level: national-technical"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#topConceptOf": [
