  {
    "@id": "https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/NaturraumregionenSTMK/mMT",
    "@type": [
      "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept"
    ],
    "http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo": [
      {
        "@id": "http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/applicationschema/br"
      }
    ],
    "http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject": [
      {
        "@id": "http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/theme/br"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "This is the name for the Mur valley between Bruck/Mur and Graz, which is the breakthrough of the Mur through the crystallized mountain ranges of the Styrian mountains and the Graz mountains. The valley, filled with fluvial and fluvio-glacial sediments, is divided into several valley chambers separated by narrow valleys, of which the Gratwein-Gratkorner Basin was given the status of an independent sub-area. (Author: Prof. Mag. Dr. Gerhard Karl LIEB)"
      },
      {
        "@language": "de",
        "@value": "Recht gut eingebuergerte Bezeichnung fuer das Murtal zwischen Bruck/Mur und Graz, das ist der Durchbruch der Mur durch die Kristallinzuege des Steirischen Randgebirges und das Grazer Bergland. Das von fluvialen und fluvioglazialen Sedimenten erfuellte Tal gliedert sich seinem Durchbruchscharakter entsprechend in mehrere, durch Talengen voneinander getrennte Talkammern, von denen dem Gratwein-Gratkorner Becken der Rang eines selbstaendigen Teilgebietes zuerkannt wurde. (Verfasser: Prof. Mag. Dr. Gerhard Karl LIEB)"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme": [
      {
        "@id": "https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/NaturraumregionenSTMK"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation": [
      {
        "@value": "mMT"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel": [
      {
        "@language": "de",
        "@value": "Mittleres Murtal"
      },
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "middle Murtal"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "INSPIRE governance level: national-technical"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#topConceptOf": [
